      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "response",
              "name": "response",
              "value": "=üìö **Available Commands**\n\n**Configuration:**\n`::get <key>` - Get a config value\n`::set <key> <value>` - Set a config value\n\n**Information:**\n`::stats` - Show activity statistics\n`::recent [N]` - Show last N events (default 10)\n`::status` - Show your current state\n\n**System:**\n`::ping` - Test if system is working\n`::help` - Show this message\n\n**Examples:**\n`::set north_star Focus on deep work`\n`::get north_star`\n`::recent 5`",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "handle-help",
      "name": "Handle help",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
